[SN]TITLE[SN]
Rugby Union commentaries

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
BBC national and local radio provide commentary for matches from the Premiership, Pro12 league, European Champions Cup and European Challenge Cup throughout the season. Selected Pro12 games will also have live TV coverage.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
European Rugby Champions Cup
Leicester v Glasgow, 17:15 GMT (BBC Radio Leicester and BBC Radio 5 live sports extra)
European Rugby Challenge Cup
Newcastle v Ospreys, 17:00 GMT (BBC Newcastle and BBC Radio Wales)
Gloucester v Bayonne, 20:00 GMT (BBC Radio 5 live sports extra and BBC Radio Gloucestershire)
European Rugby Champions Cup
Zebre v Wasps, 15:15 GMT (BBC Coventry & Warwickshire)
Start times of commentaries and matches are subject to change at short notice.
